{"tid":1702063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本車牌你問我答之港日不同","createTime":"2019-11-09T13:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T00:32:16.000Z","uid":149342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3f18dcaff3a7237df976086e7ea9b50a526ea391","tid":1702063,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:32:39.000Z","msg":"有啲朋友問我，日本揸車同香港揸車嘅分別.我簡單啲講，就係香港人一直做緊嘅嘢，我Cap左少少圖,大家就知道根本成個概念唔同.<br />\n首先第一幅圖,係講如果條路冇斑馬線的話，基本成條路都係讓行人行先（通行を妨げてない 不能妨礙步行者通行）,如果喺香港，香港人嘅概念係行人要讓車,仲要砵尻人同屌人老母<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sc0568T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsc0568T.jpg&h=1cf52805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二幅圖係話如果有人扒你頭 ,你唔可以加速左尻人,甚至如果你發覺唔係咁夠位，你應該讓小小位俾人,呢個應該唔使講，大家都知香港人點做野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVjnpVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVjnpVB.jpg&h=cd1c5653&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n第三幅圖，係講如果路面有水或者泥,旁邊有行人的話要小心唔好噴到人，呢個又係香港人一撚定xXx,（<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BtG84VE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBtG84VE.jpg&h=585bb387&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n第四其實係平行駐車,呢個基本上係常識級別，但係香港好普遍都會見到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hzrAKVH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhzrAKVH.jpg&h=284cfbd2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢幅圖我諗係香港都好容易見到係個角位泊車，或者係巴士站泊車， YouTube大撚把片，都唔撚洗點講<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yPSPPnp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyPSPPnp.jpg&h=aab3d79a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n最後呢幅講響安，其實白色嗰個格仔係直頭講到俾你聽如果你唔你響安，係會激起前面架車嘅人嘅情緒，當然香港人響安嘅目的正正就係撩鳩人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NqkhYfM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNqkhYfM.jpg&h=d3c98e43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dd364fa978fde603f230544758c0c6c09decdcc","tid":1702063,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"第二點我試過<br />\n小路夾大路<br />\n香港要慢慢吉出去<br />\n我第一次去到佢地停左黎讓我<br />\n搞到我果下唔知點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要我係入高速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果下幾唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e743c575505abafca4ef3c853baff1313f64dbd4","tid":1702063,"uid":149342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7dd364fa978fde603f230544758c0c6c09decdcc","tid":1702063,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"第二點我試過<br />\n小路夾大路<br />\n香港要慢慢吉出去<br />\n我第一次去到佢地停左黎讓我<br />\n搞到我果下唔知點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要我係入高速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果下幾唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UK9bioc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUK9bioc.jpg&h=dd26dadb&s={SIZE}\" /> 我幅圖cap得衰,幅圖下面其實寫住避讓義務,基本上唔讓係錯,呢樣同香港人嘅concept 都幾相反"},{"pid":"cb27691e13ad82b2e50e6597558e5d37401d2b4b","tid":1702063,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:44:56.000Z","msg":"點睇俾人推？<br />\n其實都唔係特登 係有時慣咗手勢跟得貼"},{"pid":"fde971401adc561a6b6bec2d9919f7c84511e4b2","tid":1702063,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb27691e13ad82b2e50e6597558e5d37401d2b4b","tid":1702063,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:44:56.000Z","msg":"點睇俾人推？<br />\n其實都唔係特登 係有時慣咗手勢跟得貼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VmOfK7y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVmOfK7y.jpg&h=a62b21de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0f1ebbd1fd2868390955504ef3d2fb1091f971a","tid":1702063,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:57:55.000Z","msg":"其實你講既都唔關邊個國家車牌先<br />\n係應該渣車本身要咁, 人地只係跟足晒<br />\n係應該叫香港人去日本渣車唔好帶埋D 陋習過去<br />\n<br />\n真係唔同都應該提下左轉同時行人路會係綠燈<br />\n十字路口轉右要等對面線過..etc"},{"pid":"b3df76893b1515d1c2d1b0d4b4334e5681df0fa7","tid":1702063,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"你拎日本本menu出黎睇.....其實香港本menu都寫得幾靚架..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82ebd42376ac6ee7f60cdbd8e41579e79a30c46","tid":1702063,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fde971401adc561a6b6bec2d9919f7c84511e4b2","tid":1702063,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb27691e13ad82b2e50e6597558e5d37401d2b4b","tid":1702063,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:44:56.000Z","msg":"點睇俾人推？<br />\n其實都唔係特登 係有時慣咗手勢跟得貼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VmOfK7y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVmOfK7y.jpg&h=a62b21de&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3F1XYvg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3F1XYvg.png&h=b39b6baa&s={SIZE}\" /> 車間距離つめて，推車，基本上不會做"},{"pid":"95bae4768124df5f1a461991732c97532bfa06d4","tid":1702063,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3df76893b1515d1c2d1b0d4b4334e5681df0fa7","tid":1702063,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"你拎日本本menu出黎睇.....其實香港本menu都寫得幾靚架..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:03:57.000Z","msg":"咪玩,香港筆試我都考過,求撚其ga woo"},{"pid":"2cf1712d9b53b58cc1928fea0